  "detailed_description": "You are humanity’s last line of defense in this retro-inspired deckbuilder. Every hand brings you one step closer to victory against the waves of <strong>SPACE INVADERS</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step onto the bridge of a Cannon class heavy frigate. Outsmart the invading forces and rival commanders all vying for <strong>HI-SCORE</strong> dominance.  Rise up the ranks in this strategic multiplayer card game based on the iconic arcade classic.<br><br>The deck is yours, Commander!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/e1fcffbef83204f08847cdda9e4a6ee7.webp?t=1772028448\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/e1fcffbef83204f08847cdda9e4a6ee7.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=60 /></picture></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/6632e8e982ea1e6aade8a37f414a7364.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=610 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/6632e8e982ea1e6aade8a37f414a7364.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><i>SPACE INVADERS: Deck Commander</i> is a fast-paced, strategic deck-builder.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/63e898d242e4b9b6030dc0395c9b9863.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/63e898d242e4b9b6030dc0395c9b9863.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/63e898d242e4b9b6030dc0395c9b9863.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>You begin with a small deck of basic cards used to power your ship.  Every turn you discover new action cards to customize your deck and form new strategies.  Balance your deck to maximize your score multiplier and keep the <strong>INVADERS</strong> at bay.  Create your own powerful action combos to outmaneuver rival Commanders and gain <strong>HI-SCORE</strong>.  Be the first to take out the mysterious <strong>UFO</strong> to complete the wave and stop the invasion.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/8eb56b5617321dbab6e2bb536803eee7.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/8eb56b5617321dbab6e2bb536803eee7.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/8eb56b5617321dbab6e2bb536803eee7.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Compete against friends online to gain <strong>RANK</strong> and climb the leaderboards or you can practice offline against bots.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/00d455010876f3abfadffabd38b82cd4.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=610 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/00d455010876f3abfadffabd38b82cd4.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic deck building action for both new and experienced card players.<br></li><li>Discover new and powerful card combinations in every match.<br></li><li>Fast-paced gameplay perfect for quick action-packed sessions.<br></li><li>Take on your friends and enemies in ranked online matches for 2 to 4 players.<br></li><li>Online leaderboards where you compete with the world.<br></li><li>Practice your command skills and card combos against challenging bots.<br></li><li>More secrets to be revealed soon...</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>The INVASION is coming!",
  "about_the_game": "You are humanity’s last line of defense in this retro-inspired deckbuilder. Every hand brings you one step closer to victory against the waves of <strong>SPACE INVADERS</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/292e87279738f739ff0b91ad585714ae.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step onto the bridge of a Cannon class heavy frigate. Outsmart the invading forces and rival commanders all vying for <strong>HI-SCORE</strong> dominance.  Rise up the ranks in this strategic multiplayer card game based on the iconic arcade classic.<br><br>The deck is yours, Commander!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/e1fcffbef83204f08847cdda9e4a6ee7.webp?t=1772028448\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/e1fcffbef83204f08847cdda9e4a6ee7.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" class=\"bb_img\" width=610 height=60 /></picture></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/6632e8e982ea1e6aade8a37f414a7364.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=610 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/6632e8e982ea1e6aade8a37f414a7364.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><