r><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/00d455010876f3abfadffabd38b82cd4.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=610 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/00d455010876f3abfadffabd38b82cd4.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic deck building action for both new and experienced card players.<br></li><li>Discover new and powerful card combinations in every match.<br></li><li>Fast-paced gameplay perfect for quick action-packed sessions.<br></li><li>Take on your friends and enemies in ranked online matches for 2 to 4 players.<br></li><li>Online leaderboards where you compete with the world.<br></li><li>Practice your command skills and card combos against challenging bots.<br></li><li>More secrets to be revealed soon...</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.poster.avif?t=1772028448\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.webm?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060310/extras/768d0a9ad5c747ab32bacc1b9eba1627.mp4?t=1772028448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>The INVASION is coming!",
